        {
            "title": "日本選戰將拉開大幕 高市早苗支持率略有下滑",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗攝影師：Kiyoshi Ota/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eIUPMx12UopLIMEaMA48lA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8ed52a24a7eb50117dae4050917d4cc7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:高市;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/高市\">高市</a>早苗攝影師：Kiyoshi Ota/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 周末進行的幾項民意調查顯示，日本首相高市早苗的支持率略有下降，表明她在2月初提前選舉的決定存在風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">民調初步展現了選民對高市早苗上周宣布提前大選的看法。儘管按歷史標準來看，她的支持率仍然相當高，但出現一定下滑表明部分選民並不認同她提前大選的決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">共同社的民調顯示，高市早苗的支持率下滑4個百分點至63%；讀賣新聞的民調顯示，她的支持率下滑4個百分點至69%；ANN的民調顯示，其支持率下滑5.4個百分點至57.6%。日經新聞和每日新聞民調顯示的高市早苗支持率降幅更大，前者下降8個百分點至67%，後者下降10個百分點至57%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f5da65fc-2239-3b63-8e5d-ebbafd3c3af7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在周一下午舉行的黨首辯論中，高市早苗對支持率下滑不以為然。相反，她態度強硬地賭上自己的首相之位。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果自民黨和維新會不能贏得多數席位，我將立即辭職，」她說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《每日新聞》的報導顯示，41%的受訪者不認同高市早苗解散國會的時機，因為那恰逢國會例會開幕日，將不可避免地導致始於4月新財年的預算推遲通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過儘管有所下滑，但高市早苗的支持率在一些民調中仍保持在60%以上，表明她仍然擁有相當高的人氣，也讓她有一定的回旋餘地。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本首相高市早苗確認將於2月8日舉行提前選舉</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原最大在野黨立憲民主黨和自民黨的前執政聯盟夥伴公明黨合併組建的新政黨「中道改革聯合」，儘管努力挑戰執政黨，但似乎進展艱難。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ANN的民調顯示，26%的受訪者對中道改革聯合抱有希望，而62%的人表示不抱希望。讀賣新聞的調查也呈現出類似趨勢，22%的受訪者表示抱有希望，69%則表示對其不抱希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">正式競選活動將於周二開始，選民將於2月8日前往投票站投票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Takaichi’s Ratings Dip as Japan Heads Into Election Campaign</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0%E5%B0%87%E6%8B%89%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%95-%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%8E%87%E7%95%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-080445031.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 21:04:30",
