        },
        {
            "title": "香港將人民幣業務資金安排額度提高一倍 協助銀行拓展人民幣業務",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"PBOC, Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"524\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q3FS4.qL6uALxJF2_sisUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2df8ce1f7239ef6c10aaa21098a9877f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">PBOC, Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 香港將把可供銀行借用的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人民幣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人民幣\">人民幣</a>資金供應量增加一倍，這項最新舉措是為滿足不斷成長的需求，並幫助中國提升人民幣在全球的使用率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港金融管理局周一宣布，「人民幣業務資金安排」的總額度將由目前的1,000億元人民幣，增加至2,000億元，新額度將於2月2日起生效。這項安排允許銀行從香港金管局獲得期限不超過一年的貸款，以上海銀行間同業拆放利率(Shibor)為定價基準。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金管局在聲明中表示，自2025年10月推出人民幣業務資金安排以來，「銀行業界反應踴躍」，1,000億元人民幣的總額度已全數分配給40家參與銀行。聲明稱，這項安排除了服務香港的企業，更成功將離岸人民幣資金輻射到東協、中東和歐洲等地。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-40ba3978-9a52-3a81-bd6a-1516fe05c603-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鑒於人民幣的借貸成本低於美元和歐元，全球對人民幣融資的需求近年來增加。擴大後的計畫將有助於香港鞏固其作為領先離岸人民幣樞紐的地位，並有助於中國推動人民幣國際化的努力。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">渣打集團中國宏觀策略主管劉潔表示，這一消息比預期來得早得多，表明離岸市場對人民幣流動性的需求強於預期，因為較低的利率使人民幣成為更具吸引力的融資貨幣。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"524\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ATkfvFEcTKNGqYbJv5VCQQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUyNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/45525debff49292c89ce65f8fbdf7b4c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hong Kong Boosts Yuan Supply to Banks in Push for China Currency</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Iris Ouyang.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E9%A1%8D%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98-%E5%80%8D-%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99-065817396.html",
