        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利稱英國受人工智能裁員衝擊最重 崗位淨流失超過德、日等國",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Morgan Stanley Research\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"491\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yQoHVJBFlWknrmRDGZeLVA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ5MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e5d58bd31ed77b2d9c28bb168de4e956\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Morgan Stanley Research</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 根據摩根士丹利的研究，英國因人工智能(AI)喪失的工作崗位數量，已超過其創造的工作崗位數量，而且崗位流失速度快於國際上的類似經濟體。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該研究發現，儘管企業採用AI技術帶來了顯著效益，但英國勞動者為此承受了尤為沉重的代價，本來就趨冷的勞動力市場雪上加霜。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">向彭博披露的這份研究表明，英國企業報告稱，在過去12個月AI導致就業崗位淨減少8%。在涵蓋德國、美國、日本和澳大利亞企業的組別中，英國企業的這一比例最高，且為國際平均水平的兩倍。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6cbe0ffc-2037-3bf5-b265-1d1d29e1b5bd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"491\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/B2nB3zMvUOaxXJke3L1zXQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ5MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/dbd62c1d350acd02b1f2ffd1c3a0d19e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告調查了已使用人工智能至少一年的企業，覆蓋對AI敏感的五大行業：消費必需品與零售、房地產、交通運輸、醫療設備及汽車行業。對其中許多企業而言，技術投資已經初見成效。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國企業因表示，AI平均而言帶來了11.5%的生產力提升，其中近半數企業報告的增幅更大。美國企業實現幾乎相同幅度的生產力提升，但因人工智能而創造的就業崗位比裁減的崗位更多。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博對英國國家統計局線上職位空缺數據的分析顯示，雖然各行業招聘職位普遍減少，但英國企業正以明顯更快的速度縮減那些可能受到AI影響的職位，包括軟件開發人員和諮詢顧問。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"996\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cxiJwhPx_j_famn9Vpj3pA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk5Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fd90df3bd1e7c8490c73489fb9823f56\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利的研究還顯示，接受調查的雇主在英國最有可能裁減需要兩到五年工作經驗的初級崗位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該研究合著者、駐倫敦的歐洲、中東和非洲地區可持續發展研究主管Rachel Fletcher表示，這些發現為人工智能將如何重塑勞動力市場提供了「早期預警信號」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題AI Job Cuts Are Landing Hardest in Britain, Morgan Stanley Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%97%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E6%9C%80%E9%87%8D-%E5%B4%97%E4%BD%8D%E6%B7%A8%E6%B5%81%E5%A4%B1%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%B7-%E6%97%A5%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%8B-062851581.html",
